    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project or a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical character. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all major components remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to bring it back to its best. It\u2019s an honest car at a fair price for those looking for value.",
      "price": 23500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
